- Story? Ours?

155
00:13:25,833 --> 00:13:28,999
Every one has a story.

156
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:33,083
So when we meet others, our stories meet

157
00:13:33,833 --> 00:13:36,832
We'll spend lots of time together and

158
00:13:36,833 --> 00:13:39,499
We'll look each other up in New York

159
00:13:39,500 --> 00:13:44,417
