I never thought of you that way

217
00:19:56,292 --> 00:20:02,375
Sounds fine, but it
never came to my mind

218
00:20:04,167 --> 00:20:08,667
and soon nothing about
you is good enough"

219
00:20:09,042 --> 00:20:10,791
What an awful shirt

220
