What a haircut

221
00:20:12,458 --> 00:20:14,083
Stop speeding

222
00:20:14,084 --> 00:20:15,457
Stop hogging

223
00:20:15,458 --> 00:20:16,415
Give me a break

224
00:20:16,416 --> 00:20:20,833
"Up close she wants to change your life

225
00:20:21,333 --> 00:20:25,833
the spell she casts can ruin your life"

226
00:20:26,291 --> 00:20:30,708
"You'll fall for her words
then you'll know why..."

227
00:20:31,209 --> 00:20:35,209
"what started with
a laugh ends in a cry"

228
00:20:35,458 --> 00:20:46,084
"And you'll never figure why
she's so unlike a guy"

229
00:21:15,500 --> 00:21:19,917
