what makes you such a flirt?"

230
00:21:20,416 --> 00:21:25,042
"The thousand gifts you shower on her
for what were all those flowers?"

231
00:21:25,416 --> 00:21:27,457
You didn't tell me your name

232
00:21:27,458 --> 00:21:28,874
How about a coffee?

233
00:21:28,875 --> 00:21:31,249
Can I drop you home?

234
00:21:31,250 --> 00:21:32,749
When do I get to see you next?

235
00:21:32,750 --> 00:21:37,042
"It's a wayward life you've
lived living like a tramp"

236
00:21:37,583 --> 00:21:42,084
"But you'll insist you're different
why are you so vain?"

237
00:21:42,583 --> 00:21:44,415
That wet towel on the floor

238
00:21:44,416 --> 00:21:46,083
Cap of the toothpaste tube missing

239
00:21:46,084 --> 00:21:48,083
Wear used socks inside out

240
00:21:48,084 --> 00:21:49,958
Never knows how time flies?

241
00:21:49,959 --> 00:21:54,416
"How to live a life, she shows you"

242
00:21:54,708 --> 00:21:59,291
"She makes something human out of you"

243
00:22:04,583 --> 00:22:08,708
"And she knows what
you can't tell her"

244
00:22:08,917 --> 00:22:19,291
"That's just why no girl's are like a guy"

245
00:22:24,583 --> 00:22:29,000
"All sorts of strange dates
she'll always call to mind"

246
00:22:29,416 --> 00:22:33,917
"Love can be forgotten
but forgetting a date is crime"

247
00:22:34,166 --> 00:22:37,875
On 1st March, we looked at each other.
4th April, I went to meet you

248
00:22:38,125 --> 00:22:40,124
