250
00:22:41,875 --> 00:22:46,250
"Can't trust a guy,
these guys are so fast"

251
00:22:46,750 --> 00:22:51,375
"Now he's here, now he's gone
no telling how long he'll last"

252
00:22:51,917 --> 00:22:54,958
